      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FLAMIN' JOE (1) finished in the placings last time but could not have been more impressive three back in his brilliant 18.96 win at this track over 340m. Can return to winning form here if runs up to best figures. HARD STYLE GIRL (4) finished third (22.67) two back at this track but out of the placings last time when 7th at Wentworth Park. Form here at the trip sound including three wins. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings five times from eight starts. Should be about the money. ZIPPING MARQUEZ (8) goes very well this trip starting 14 times for five wins and four minors. In the money last time at Wentworth Park (30.06) in a Grade 5, finishing a 6 length third. Can hit the frame with the right run. DYNAMIC DRUMMER (5) cannot be underestimated.",
